1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] I zato Isus kaže farizeima,ja znam vi se nećete obratiti jer vi me slušate ali nećete da me čujete,nećete da razmišljate ono što ja vam kažu i nećete kažet da onda prihvatite pa da vas ja izliječim,a to je grozno.

2
00:00:15,000 --> 00:00:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] A mi zaboravljamo zapravo da Isus tako strašno kritizirao farizeje,zašto?

3
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa zato što smo mi svi farizeji.

4
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja nisam među kršćanima naš neko ko nije farizej,šta to znači?

5
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] Farizej je čovjek koji čuje propovjede,a nikad se ne mijenja na njoj.

6
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sli slušali da nalazim na mislije šta je bilo propovjed?

7
00:00:35,000 --> 00:00:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] Šta je rekao župlik?

8
00:00:37,000 --> 00:00:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] Joj ne znam.

9
00:00:39,000 --> 00:00:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kažu veći murci.

10
00:00:42,000 --> 00:00:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] Krvosno.

11
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam pokušam,od propovjedam pa doćem od doba i kažem čekaj šta se nalazim propovjedom?

12
00:00:49,000 --> 00:00:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kao da imaš neke praznire čekaj da nesličam se neke stvari.

13
00:00:54,000 --> 00:00:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da se onam potrude da to izvadim.

14
00:00:56,000 --> 00:00:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] I tad shvatim zašto Isus kaže.

15
00:00:59,000 --> 00:01:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] Četiri sjemena ja bacim samo jedno i jedno donese propovjed.

16
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jedna riječ,jedna propovjed patne po kraj puta i ptice,ko da ti neko odnije.

17
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sve pitan kako to mogu zaboraviti.

18
00:01:11,000 --> 00:01:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] zaboraviti.

19
00:01:12,000 --> 00:01:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kad pročitam u većanjaku ovo me u glasom sila bilo, to zapamtim.

20
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kad mi neko od vas priča, pa zapamtim za sto godina.

21
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali kad pročitam svetog pisma, kada čujem neku propovjed, gotovo je.

22
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] Odija iz crkve, nemaju.

23
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] To su rijetke koji čuju, pa da to ostane u njima.

24
00:01:29,000 --> 00:01:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je ono najbolje zlodake.

25
00:01:32,000 --> 00:01:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jedno pozobaju ptice.

26
00:01:33,000 --> 00:01:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] Isus kaže, to je džava koji dođe i uzme riječ iz tebe da ne to ne se proda.

27
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] Drugo kaže, on padne na kamion.

28
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] To znači oduševiš.

29
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] I joj što je dobro govorio.

30
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Joj ovo bi trebalo.

31
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa da baš bi trebalo.

32
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa da bi to čuli oni moji susjedi.

33
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] Joj baš bi trebalo.

34
00:01:49,000 --> 00:01:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne bude oko pol sata.

35
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] Šta je ono bilo?

36
00:01:52,000 --> 00:01:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ma daj pusti, ajde.

37
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zaboraviš.

38
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] Treće, padne u trdnje.

39
00:01:57,000 --> 00:01:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] Je tvoje brige.

40
00:01:59,000 --> 00:02:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] Joj moram ovo, moram ono, moram ono.

41
00:02:01,000 --> 00:02:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] Šta je župnik ono rekao?

42
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ma pusti župnik.

43
00:02:04,000 --> 00:02:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ajde, moram kuhat juhu.

44
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] I tako dalje.

45
00:02:07,000 --> 00:02:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sve ne.

46
00:02:08,000 --> 00:02:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tek četvrto sjeme.

47
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ajde, probajte malo mislit.

48
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko već dugo dolazite ovam četvrtku?

49
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jel li vas i jedan četvrtak promijenio?

50
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nije dobro da bi sami se mi kažeš ja sam promijenio.

51
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znate, mene najgore je kad oni dođu pa svjedočaj zato ja sam se promijenio.

52
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tako ima ne vjerujem.

53
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja vjerujem samo onime za koje drugi kažu.

54
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jeste, taj se izbilja promijenio.

55
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pitaj svoga muža šta on misli.

56
00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jeste ti promijenio?

57
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] Reče da jesi, ali na zlo, jel?

58
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] A na dobro?

59
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pitaj svoju ženu ženu.

60
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jesam li ja štogod bolji?

61
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] Joj mužu, tvoja starost ubi tebe i mene.

62
00:02:53,000 --> 00:02:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] Mi smo svjesni zapravo toga koliko farizeizma ima u svima namirka.

63
00:02:58,000 --> 00:03:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kako je strašno napor ako hoćeš napredovati u životu.

64
00:03:01,000 --> 00:03:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] Mi preolako prihvatimo to.

65
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] O, ja idem na misli uve čast.

66
00:03:06,000 --> 00:03:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] O, pa ja ću sigurno u nebo.

67
00:03:07,000 --> 00:03:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znate šta?

68
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja obavljam prve petke.

69
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] Devet prvi petake.

70
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] Gospa je rekla preko svete Margarite.

71
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] Finok, kad ja budem umirala, dođe sigurno svečeniki odrešit će mi.

72
00:03:17,000 --> 00:03:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jo, ne.

73
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne hoćeš, jarce.

74
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] To Isus nigde ni rekao.

75
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kad budeš umirao, zove ispovednika pa će te u nebo vesti.

76
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] u nebo vesti.

77
00:03:28,000 --> 00:03:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne.

78
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nego tko čuva moju riječ, staj me ljubi.

79
00:03:31,000 --> 00:03:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] I k njemu ćemo doći.

80
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kod njega se nastanete.

81
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] Neće o nekoj govori gospodine, gospodine, uče kraljice o nebeskom.

82
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nego neko vrši vode nebeskog oca.

83
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tko vrši ono što ti sad ne staš.

84
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tko izvrši ono što ste čuli večeras ovdje u kinoteci.

85
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Šta vredi inače?

86
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kinoteka će se ispraziti ako vi ne budete drugačiji za sljedeći četvrtak.

87
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto mi neko dolazio u kinodeju kad vidi:

88
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] To su iste ovce.

89
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jarca si mi dao, Jarca ti vraća, kaže.

90
00:03:56,000 --> 00:03:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne zvukni čovjek.

91
00:03:57,000 --> 00:04:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ako ide se ti promijenio na bolje, drugačiji, si zdraviji, sve ti...

92
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] Gdje si to dobio?

93
00:04:04,000 --> 00:04:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] Četvrtko?

94
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ma ide mi ja čovjek, šta je to?

95
00:04:06,000 --> 00:04:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ko to govori?

96
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ma ima neki tamo čuni čovjek.

97
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali dobro govori.

98
00:04:11,000 --> 00:04:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ono ćeš moći reći.

99
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] Prijatelji, lako je obratiti svijet,

100
00:04:17,000 --> 00:04:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] ali teško je te obratiti.

101
00:04:19,000 --> 00:04:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da ja tebe obratio,

102
00:04:21,000 --> 00:04:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zagreb mi je bio cijeli obraćan.

103
00:04:24,000 --> 00:04:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] A kad ste vi svi dobri, šta ću od svaki?

104
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali probajmo večera, svaki od nas.

105
00:04:33,000 --> 00:04:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] Uzmi te bar jedno, u čemu se ti večera možeš popraviti?

106
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] Čemu ćeš nešto promijeniti?

107
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa savježbaj tri dana, vidjet ćeš.

108
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] Garantiran ti.

109
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] Neko će u tvojoj kući reći:

110
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Skoro se promijenio.

111
00:04:46,000 --> 00:04:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kad neko kaže:

112
00:04:48,000 --> 00:04:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam se večasni obratio.

113
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] Rekao, pita ću ja tvoju ženu.

114
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] Onda kad mi ona potvrdi:

115
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] Je večasni, stvarno je drugačiji.

116
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] E onda da, onda vjeruje.

117
00:04:58,000 --> 00:05:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] E to mogu biti tvoji doživlja i emocije.

118
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa nije to.

119
00:05:03,000 --> 00:05:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] Onda mi još dođeš tu pa mi pričaš.

120
00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam se obratio.

121
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ljudi si spavljaju.

122
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pričaj ti.

123
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dovedi nekog drugog i da o tebi govori.

124
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] E to je onda svjedočenje.

125
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svjedoči se za drugog, ne za sebi.

126
00:05:15,000 --> 00:05:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ko to još zove tebe da svjedočiš za sebe na sudu?

127
00:05:19,000 --> 00:05:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jel da ne?

128
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] Moraš vaći kog drugog koji svjedoči se.

129
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] A mi se svjedoči ostavljaju za sebe.

130
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dođeš i pričaš.

131
00:05:25,000 --> 00:05:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] O, ja sam bio zločeš.

132
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] A ja nisam bio nikom.

133
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja nisam bio.

134
00:05:28,000 --> 00:05:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam uzman drugog.

135
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam alkohol.

136
00:05:30,000 --> 00:05:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam s ovo.

137
00:05:31,000 --> 00:05:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] I sad ja ne pisao.

138
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne uzim alkohol.

139
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ma daj, če ne uzmaš.

140
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne uzmaš sada do govoriš.

141
00:05:35,000 --> 00:05:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] A poslika dođeš doma.

142
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali kad to drugi kaže koji te vide tamo kad si kako sluše.

143
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] Onda se stvari mijenjaju.

144
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] Agioterapija dakle radi na tom duhovnom području.

145
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] On radi o bitku.

146
00:05:55,000 --> 00:05:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] I kaže bitak je jedan, istinit, dobar i lijepo.

147
00:05:59,000 --> 00:06:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] I kad si ti u tom bitku.

148
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je Bog.

149
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] Teologija kaže bitak.

150
00:06:04,000 --> 00:06:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je sve moguće stvoriti.

151
00:06:05,000 --> 00:06:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je osoba.

152
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je netko.

153
00:06:07,000 --> 00:06:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ti si onda u njemu.

154
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] I tako se spaši.

155
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] I zato ćemo sa mi začutiti prijatelji dragi.

156
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da kad dođete pred svjetog petra će reći štaviti u nebo.

157
00:06:15,000 --> 00:06:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kako?

158
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ko si ti?

159
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] O, ja sam ti išao svakog četvrtka.

160
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ono mi i vančite tamo.

161
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] A ja sam išao u katedraru na misle.

162
00:06:21,000 --> 00:06:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] O, ja sam i do devet prvi petak obavio pet puta.

163
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] O, ja sam ti molio krunicu svaki drugi dan.

164
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] A ja sam prije jela i molio.

165
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] A ja nekom išao u crkvu.

166
00:06:29,000 --> 00:06:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] On će reći.

167
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] Žao mi je.

168
00:06:31,000 --> 00:06:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] Moj šef rekao da farizeji ne idu u nebo.

169
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kako farizeji?

170
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ja išao u crkvu.

171
00:06:37,000 --> 00:06:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] Išao si u crkvu.

172
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa možete ići sto puta u apoteku.

173
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] Al nisim jedna puta uzdo lijekove.

174
00:06:42,000 --> 00:06:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ušao je rekao dobar dan u apoteku i otišao dobar.

175
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je na misle.

176
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] Šta to vrijedno?

177
00:06:50,000 --> 00:06:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa je da ste izvrgljao.

178
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zdrav Mariju sveta Mariju.

179
00:06:54,000 --> 00:06:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zdrav Mariju sveta Mariju.

180
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jo, Marija to nikad i našao tamo.

181
00:06:57,000 --> 00:07:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da razgovara s tobom i da budete zajedni.

182
00:07:00,000 --> 00:07:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bezbroj stvari.

183
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] Govorim vam tako o primjerima i ovako malo šatrovački.

184
00:07:05,000 --> 00:07:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kako bismo što jasnije vidjeli.

185
00:07:07,000 --> 00:07:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko se mi varamo kad uđemo u bit svoga života i vjera.

186
00:07:12,000 --> 00:07:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jako varamo.

187
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] I zato treba raskrinkati to što mi mislimo da je vjera.

188
00:07:17,000 --> 00:07:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] To nije to.

189
00:07:18,000 --> 00:07:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nešto sasvim drugo.

190
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nešto sasvim ljepše.

191
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] U njoj se uživa.

192
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle.

193
00:07:27,000 --> 00:07:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] Hadioterapija nas želi osvijestiti.

194
00:07:30,000 --> 00:07:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da nam pokaže.

195
00:07:32,000 --> 00:07:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da bolesti duhovne duše.

196
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] To nije ono što mi obično mislimo.

197
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] Malo šizofrenije.

198
00:07:37,000 --> 00:07:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] Malo depresije.

199
00:07:38,000 --> 00:07:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] Malo suicida.

200
00:07:39,000 --> 00:07:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] E to je ovo što je skriveno zapravo ispod vanjskog plašta.

201
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] Gdje je najveći progno recimo meni?

202
00:07:46,000 --> 00:07:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] Hadioasistenata.

203
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] U svim centrima za hadioterapiju.

204
00:07:50,000 --> 00:07:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] Upravo tome što oni misle da su oni pravi.

205
00:07:53,000 --> 00:07:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tek kad pacijent vidi da su oni promijenili onda će on željeti doći k njima i onda će on se predati.

206
00:07:59,000 --> 00:08:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bez promjene u životu ne postoji mogućnost da ikoga promijeniš.

207
00:08:03,000 --> 00:08:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] A isto vremeno ne moguće je promijeniti se pa da se drugi ne mijenjaju kraj tebe.

208
00:08:08,000 --> 00:08:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svatite tu to pravilo.

209
00:08:10,000 --> 00:08:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nemoguće je da se ti promijeniš pa da se drugi ne mijenjaju.

210
00:08:16,000 --> 00:08:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da mijenjaju se raditi na sebi je zapravo bitno.

211
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tada mijenjaš sebe i ti si sretan i zdrav, a mijenjaš drugi oko sebe.

212
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] promijeni.

213
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] To će mi problem.

214
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] A je težava je kad mi dođe majka:

215
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] "A moj sin se drogira koliko na godina?"

216
00:08:32,000 --> 00:08:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] "35.

217
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nije nikad završio studij, ne radi, znate.

218
00:08:37,000 --> 00:08:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] Šta da radim s njima?"

219
00:08:38,000 --> 00:08:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Pa majko, dajte one četiri, znate, točke."

220
00:08:42,000 --> 00:08:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Pa molim."

221
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Pa zato je tako."

222
00:08:45,000 --> 00:08:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Pa kako to?"

223
00:08:46,000 --> 00:08:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Pa ko on rekao da se molitom rješava problem vašeg sina i droge?"

224
00:08:50,000 --> 00:08:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Ima to negdje?"

225
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Još nisam vidio."

226
00:08:53,000 --> 00:08:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] Isus nigde ne kaže u evanđelu:

227
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Moli, pa će ti fino rješiti sve probleme."

228
00:08:57,000 --> 00:08:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Pa li rekao:

229
00:08:59,000 --> 00:09:00,000
[UNKNOWN] "Vjero."

230
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Majko, vjeruješ li da tvoj sin može biti drugačiji?"

231
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Promijeni se prema njemu."

232
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Vjeruješ li da u njemu ima nešto dobrota i da bi još hitio biti drugačiji?"

233
00:09:11,000 --> 00:09:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] "I se li će ti promijenila prema njemu?"

234
00:09:16,000 --> 00:09:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] "I ovdje časnije:

235
00:09:18,000 --> 00:09:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Znate, pa to je ne može..."

236
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Dajte vi molite za njega."

237
00:09:20,000 --> 00:09:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Pa može da onda ja dokažem da mi može ništa."

238
00:09:23,000 --> 00:09:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Pa šta, da vi pomozite mi?"

239
00:09:25,000 --> 00:09:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Neću ja ništa moliti, ba."

240
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Ti se majko promijeni i točka."

241
00:09:29,000 --> 00:09:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Nemoguće promijeniti se na bolje,

242
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] a da se drugi oko tebe ne mijenje."

243
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Protom, ako vidiš da drugi pada i u sve veće zlo,

244
00:09:38,000 --> 00:09:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] da ti djeca ili unuci postoji sve zlo česti,

245
00:09:40,000 --> 00:09:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] paziti, nešto u tebi nije u redu."

246
00:09:45,000 --> 00:09:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] toga budimo svjesno.

247
00:09:47,000 --> 00:09:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] "U tebi nešto nije u redu."

248
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Ako jedva Hrvatsko društvo ne funkcionira, da je zločiško, paziti,

249
00:09:53,000 --> 00:09:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] mi kršćani nešto s nama nije u redu."

250
00:09:55,000 --> 00:09:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Jel mi smo duša društva."

251
00:09:57,000 --> 00:09:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Kaže koncila."

252
00:09:59,000 --> 00:10:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] "I to nije nešto gdje biste vi sad trebali mijenjati svijet."

253
00:10:03,000 --> 00:10:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Oslovodi Bože da vi mijenjate svijet."

254
00:10:05,000 --> 00:10:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Jel bi ima pobjegu iz toga svijeta."

255
00:10:07,000 --> 00:10:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Nego sebe mijenjati."

256
00:10:09,000 --> 00:10:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] "I to nije nešto strašno."

257
00:10:10,000 --> 00:10:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Ma svakog veče mešta."

258
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Svakog četvrtka."

259
00:10:12,000 --> 00:10:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Edu malu."

260
00:10:13,000 --> 00:10:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Aj makar mali potezič promijeni se."

261
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] "U čemu?"

262
00:10:15,000 --> 00:10:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Nauči bar obraždati."

263
00:10:17,000 --> 00:10:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Aj nauči svaki dan ono sebi...

264
00:10:19,000 --> 00:10:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Jo, žal mi jo."

265
00:10:20,000 --> 00:10:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] "I dok ne vediš da si istisno iz sebe nekog si povrijedio."

266
00:10:24,000 --> 00:10:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Žal mi jo, prosti mi."

267
00:10:25,000 --> 00:10:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] "I tako dalje."

268
00:10:26,000 --> 00:10:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Govoriš u sebi dok ne vidiš si slobodan."

269
00:10:28,000 --> 00:10:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Maj prvi to vidjet ćeš."

270
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Jeg probaj bar uvesi to da uvijek pohvališ one koji su kvotkri."

271
00:10:34,000 --> 00:10:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] "To sad si muže ugorla:

272
00:10:35,000 --> 00:10:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Joj, kako ti to izgledaš?"

273
00:10:36,000 --> 00:10:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Ajde, kačeš bricić."

274
00:10:37,000 --> 00:10:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Pa opet se nisi obrijao."

275
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Pa vidi kako ti izgledaju cipele."

276
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Pa vječki ti ja moram tu tvoju krevatu slagati."

277
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Joj, muže, što uživam kad ti mogu složiti krevatu."

278
00:10:46,000 --> 00:10:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Dje molite, skini cipele."

279
00:10:48,000 --> 00:10:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Joj, poljubit ću ti noge i očisti cipele."

280
00:10:51,000 --> 00:10:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Tako bi moj šep Isus napravio."

281
00:10:56,000 --> 00:11:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] "I ti se ozoveš Kršanka, a on Židom."

282
00:11:01,000 --> 00:11:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Garantirati."

283
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Reci jednu toplu riječ.

284
00:11:09,000 --> 00:11:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Nauči se govoriti uvek pozitivno."

285
00:11:11,000 --> 00:11:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Garantiram da ćeš biti."

286
00:11:13,000 --> 00:11:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] "I svaki dan to doživljujem."

287
00:11:16,000 --> 00:11:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] "To je nevjerojatno."

288
00:11:17,000 --> 00:11:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Zločeci ljudima samo gledaš."

289
00:11:20,000 --> 00:11:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Movo si Isus napravio."

290
00:11:21,000 --> 00:11:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Kako si on?"

291
00:11:22,000 --> 00:11:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Oli su opet drugi ljudi."

292
00:11:24,000 --> 00:11:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Oli poču mene hvaliti."

293
00:11:25,000 --> 00:11:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Odmah nalaze sto stvari."

294
00:11:26,000 --> 00:11:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Ovo su mi posao i prijatelj."

295
00:11:27,000 --> 00:11:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Ovo, ovo."

296
00:11:28,000 --> 00:11:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] "A svakom od vas ima dobra."

297
00:11:33,000 --> 00:11:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Pa vidim na vašim očinom, vi ste sveci."

298
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Ale ne priznate si to."

299
00:11:37,000 --> 00:11:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Ne priznate si dovolite."

300
00:11:39,000 --> 00:11:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Ne ljubite sebe."

301
00:11:40,000 --> 00:11:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Ne vjerajte da jeste veliki."

302
00:11:42,000 --> 00:11:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] "I zato i dolažite jer želite biti veliki."

303
00:11:45,000 --> 00:11:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] "I jeste veliki."

304
00:11:46,000 --> 00:11:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Dakle, ajmo sad izmislite večeras."

305
00:11:49,000 --> 00:11:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Učemo da ćemo se promijeniti."

306
00:11:53,000 --> 00:11:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Do sljedećeg četvrtka."

307
00:11:54,000 --> 00:11:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Šta misliš?"

308
00:11:55,000 --> 00:11:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Što bi ti u svom životu ovaj tjedan ova napraviti?"

309
00:11:57,000 --> 00:12:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Nemojte velike stvari od odnog početka."

310
00:12:02,000 --> 00:12:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Ne prije malu neku sipu."

311
00:12:03,000 --> 00:12:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] "A onda sve veće."

312
00:12:04,000 --> 00:12:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Jer ako veliku, nemoš cijelu jednu gromadu staviti na leđa."

313
00:12:09,000 --> 00:12:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Ali malu, neću se pokreti."

314
00:12:12,000 --> 00:12:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Pokušaj se 3 dana vježbati u nekom dobru."

315
00:12:15,000 --> 00:12:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Vidiš."

316
00:12:16,000 --> 00:12:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] "To je prvi korak."

317
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Drugi korak."

318
00:12:22,000 --> 00:12:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Ajde sada, procijeni svaki dan svoj, cijelom tjednu."

319
00:12:26,000 --> 00:12:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Odaberi si u danu 15 minuta."

320
00:12:29,000 --> 00:12:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Evo, samo 15 minuta tražimo tebe."

321
00:12:31,000 --> 00:12:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] "15 minuta vremena je u kojem ćeš ti vježbati s ovome o čemu se hoćeš popraviti?"

322
00:12:39,000 --> 00:12:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] "U kojem ćeš gledati Isusa tu?"

323
00:12:41,000 --> 00:12:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Ili ako nisi vjerik, gledaš dobrotu, ljubav, kako je beskrajno."

324
00:12:46,000 --> 00:12:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Kao osoba ispred tebe."

325
00:12:48,000 --> 00:12:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Promatila ko treba 15 minuta."

326
00:12:51,000 --> 00:12:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Pokaj se."

327
00:12:53,000 --> 00:12:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Oprosti nekome."

328
00:12:56,000 --> 00:12:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Ogledaj šta možeš novo napraviti."

329
00:12:59,000 --> 00:13:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Da razmisli o nekim novim situacijama."

330
00:13:02,000 --> 00:13:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Ali 15 minuta pronađe u danu kad ti možeš 15 minuta sigurno imati."

331
00:13:06,000 --> 00:13:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Da ti to nikad ne ispada."

332
00:13:09,000 --> 00:13:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] "To je bitno."

333
00:13:10,000 --> 00:13:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Bez toga nećeš nikud se pokrenuti."

334
00:13:12,000 --> 00:13:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Pronađe u danu."

335
00:13:14,000 --> 00:13:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Jel li to od 6 do 7?"

336
00:13:15,000 --> 00:13:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Jel od 7 do 8?"

337
00:13:16,000 --> 00:13:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Jel li to 7:15, 8:15, 9:15?"

338
00:13:18,000 --> 00:13:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Jel li to najveće u 11:15 i onda zaslaš?"

339
00:13:22,000 --> 00:13:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Jel li to možda uvitro već kad se opereš, očestiš, počeš daš urediš?"

340
00:13:31,000 --> 00:13:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Jel da sjedneš ili klekneš ili tako nešto?"

341
00:13:36,000 --> 00:13:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] "15 minuta se ne daš. Sabereš te savršeno."

342
00:13:38,000 --> 00:13:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] "To je u meni. Ovo hoću. Kako da to postiđu?"

343
00:13:42,000 --> 00:13:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Pa moliš Isusa, molim te reci mi Isusa, slušaš njega."

344
00:13:45,000 --> 00:13:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Garantiram što je to beskrajno lijepo."

345
00:13:48,000 --> 00:13:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Kako je to njenja."

346
00:13:51,000 --> 00:13:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Osreću je."

347
00:13:54,000 --> 00:13:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Odredi točno vrijeme i da ti nikad ne smije spasti."

348
00:13:56,000 --> 00:13:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Pazi, to će te spasti."

349
00:13:59,000 --> 00:14:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Spasti ću te tih 15 minuta svaki jav."

350
00:14:03,000 --> 00:14:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Ako ne napraviš, 24 sata ti je uništeno."

351
00:14:06,000 --> 00:14:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Ti nikad ne moliš kako treba."

352
00:14:08,000 --> 00:14:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Nikad se nećeš da sabrati."

353
00:14:10,000 --> 00:14:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] "I nikad nećeš biti s Bogom, ni sa bitkom, ni sa sobom."

354
00:14:16,000 --> 00:14:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Moraš, 15 minuta mora biti tvoji."

355
00:14:19,000 --> 00:14:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Uredi, odredi i to niko ne smije uzeti."

356
00:14:23,000 --> 00:14:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Ko ne zatvori se u kupovnicu, sjedi u kadu, na rub kad je ne baš unutra."

357
00:14:29,000 --> 00:14:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Sada je malo sjena ispod glave, jel?"

358
00:14:32,000 --> 00:14:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] "I 15 minuta mora biti."

359
00:14:35,000 --> 00:14:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Brže se odredite koje je to vrijeme najizgodnije."

360
00:14:39,000 --> 00:14:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Kad je to sigurno da te niko neće spriječiti?"

361
00:14:44,000 --> 00:14:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Vidjet ćete, tih 15 minuta će vas dovesti do dubokog iskustva Boga i njegove blizine."

362
00:14:53,000 --> 00:14:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Do susreta s Izusom Hristo."

363
00:14:56,000 --> 00:15:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Do jednog čudesnog preokvita tvoje inteligencije, vrhonska inteligencija."

364
00:15:01,000 --> 00:15:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Sposobnost da pamtiš, gledaš, razumiješ, govoriš."

365
00:15:05,000 --> 00:15:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Nevjerojatno. 15 minuta dnevno. Promijenite."

366
00:15:09,000 --> 00:15:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Sa studentima sam to radio još 1975. godine i dalje."

367
00:15:14,000 --> 00:15:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Kad smo bili i na raznim našim godišnim skupovima izvan Zagreba, ne znam, na moru, po tri tjedna."

368
00:15:21,000 --> 00:15:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Svako jutro smo morali ti 15 minuta imati."

369
00:15:23,000 --> 00:15:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] "To ih je mijenjalo. To ih je dobro do iskustva Boga."

370
00:15:28,000 --> 00:15:29,480
[UNKNOWN] Hvala što pratite kanal.

